'''金森博雄'''（{{lang-ja|金森 博雄}}，かなもり ひろお，{{bd|1936年|10月17日|||catIdx=Aか}}），日裔美國[[地震學|地震學]]家，他對於地震的物理學和造成地震板塊運動作出了根本上的貢獻。  

==研究==
金森博雄和美國地震學家[[湯馬斯·漢克斯_(地震學家)|湯馬斯·漢克斯]]發展出更能直接反應地震過程物理性質的[[矩震級|矩震級]]，並在大規模地震時取代[[芮氏地震規模|芮氏地震規模]]<ref>Kanamori, H., (1977)</ref><ref>Utsu, T., 2001, The Seismology 3rd edition: Kyoritsu, p.138</ref>。[[昭和三陆地震|昭和三陆地震]]的矩震级即由金森博雄推算，并被[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]认可<ref name=mag>{{Cite journal |author1=Hiroo Kanamori |year=1971 |title=Seismological evidence for a lithospheric normal faulting—The Sanriku earthquake of 1933 |journal=Physics of the Earth & Planetary Interiors |volume=4 |issue=4 |language=en |pages=289-300 |url=http://www.researchgate.net/publication/222503911_Seismological_evidence_for_a_lithospheric_normal_faulting--The_Sanriku_earthquake_of_1933 |doi=10.1016/0031-9201(71)90013-6 |access-date=2018-11-03 |archive-date=2018-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103121733/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/222503911_Seismological_evidence_for_a_lithospheric_normal_faulting--The_Sanriku_earthquake_of_1933 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/official19330302173100_30/executive |title=M 8.4 - off the east coast of Honshu, Japan |publisher=[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]] |language=en |access-date=2018-11-03 |archive-date=2018-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103110401/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/official19330302173100_30/executive |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

金森博雄和[[菊地正幸|菊地正幸]]發展出了以[[遠震|遠震]]波形計算斷層上滑移分布的方式。另外，他們還研究了實時地震<ref>Kikuchi, M., and Kanamori, H. (1982)</ref><ref>Allen RM, Kanamori H. (2003)</ref><ref>Allen, R.M. and H. Kanamori (2001)</ref><ref>{{Cite book |first=Richard |last=Allen |chapter=Rapid magnitude determination for earthquake early warning |title=The Many Facets of Seismic Risk |editor=G. Manfredi, M.R. Pecce, and A. Zollo |pages=15–24 |year=2004 |series=Proceedings of the "Workshop on Multidisciplinary Approach to Seismic Risk Problems", hold in Sant'Angelo dei Lombardi, September 22, 2003 |url=http://eps.berkeley.edu/~rallen/pub/2004elarms/AllenSeismicRisk2004.pdf |access-date=2011-11-17 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701055411/http://eps.berkeley.edu/~rallen/pub/2004elarms/AllenSeismicRisk2004.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

